Board of Directors of the Company at its meeting held today i.e. Thursday 10th July 2025 has approved the following matters:
1.Unaudited Financial Results (Standalone & Consolidated) of the Company for the first quarter ended 30th June 2025;
2.Limited Review Report on unaudited financial results (standalone and consolidated) of the Company for the first quarter ended 30th June 2025 issued by Statutory Auditor M/s kkc & associates LLP Chartered Accountants.
